<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870713-0134 </DOCNO><HL> Hartmarx Share Buyback</HL><DD> 07/13/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> HMXBUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK) </IN><DATELINE> CHICAGO  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Hartmarx Corp. said its board authorized the purchase of as many as 1.5 million of the company's common shares in the open market in 1987 and 1988.    The apparel maker and retailer has 20.6 million shares outstanding. </TEXT></DOC>